+        dimensions, ignoring the last `ignore_last_ndim` axes. This is useful
+        when treating an N-D buffer as a view of its trailing sub-tensor.
+
+    Returns
+    -------
+    ptr : PrimExpr
+        A handle-typed `tir.Call` to `tl.access_ptr`.
+    """
+
